{"tid":2194148,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警長涉呃60萬貸款賭外圍  瞞騙遮仔會 廉署控四罪","createTime":"2020-09-08T10:34:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T11:28:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6e4209cce4cc40235e8251d4e2f5a6215cc0c5e8","tid":2194148,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T10:34:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200908/JEIM6MXG5BEEJGGPYCVYDHDL6U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200908%2FJEIM6MXG5BEEJGGPYCVYDHDL6U%2F&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNSBzIW6ugq8wWEqYO2LRYLo%3D&h=7da502d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200908%2FJEIM6MXG5BEEJGGPYCVYDHDL6U%2F&h=c48a06d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200908/JEIM6MXG5BEEJGGPYCVYDHDL6U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n警長涉呃60萬貸款賭外圍 <br />\n瞞騙遮仔會 廉署控四罪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/S036v0wnsohpKQaXgP_tPiBpDws=/889x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/B4VLRW57WZGAVGELCU57H3ULAQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FS036v0wnsohpKQaXgP_tPiBpDws%3D%2F889x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FB4VLRW57WZGAVGELCU57H3ULAQ.jpg&h=2da130b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■香港警察儲蓄互助社<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名先後在梁振英及林鄭月娥兩位特首任內獲頒長期服務獎章的警長，過去四年先後四次向俗稱「遮仔會」的香港警察儲蓄互助社借貸，合共60萬元。其後他被揭發申請貸款時瞞報自己在外的貸款紀錄，遭廉政公署控告四項欺詐罪。該名警長曾投注非法外圍馬，懷疑借錢與賭債有關。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：警孭債嚴重屢犯欺詐<br />\n<br />\n涉事警長為51歲的李鴻發，1988年加入警隊任職警員，2008年晉升為警長。自1988年起成為香港警察儲蓄互助社社員的他，2016年6月30日至2019年6月24日期間，先後向警察儲蓄互助社借得四筆貸款，合共60萬元。<br />\n<br />\n案情透露，李鴻發申請貸款時訛稱自己在銀行或其他財務機構並無貸款，四份貸款申請表所載的資料全部真確及完整。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n涉案非法外圍賭博經營者余泉堅（72歲）亦被控兩項收受賭注罪名，。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曾獲頒長期服務獎<br />\n<br />\n法例訂明，欺詐罪一經循公訴程序定罪，可處監禁14年。而任何人向收受賭注者投注，則可處罰款$10,000及監禁三個月。經營非法賭博則最高可判處罰款500萬元及監禁七年。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，李鴻發1999年曾因「傑出工作表現」在警察總區總部獲頒發指揮官嘉獎。他又曾先後在2013年6月獲頒香港警察長。。。。。"},{"pid":"1703539f24fb30fbd82201524dd6febfcbe1d1b9","tid":2194148,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T10:40:01.000Z","msg":"其實點解做狗既比其他紀律部隊更加鍾意賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf9b6bb189f6966baa3bec1ddba41f29d03ab230","tid":2194148,"uid":9230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T10:42:55.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦，報自己無街數。邊條重數組唔係借到尾自搵遮仔會丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4009faae1d60ed94194686451e82af7350063fd","tid":2194148,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1703539f24fb30fbd82201524dd6febfcbe1d1b9","tid":2194148,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T10:40:01.000Z","msg":"其實點解做狗既比其他紀律部隊更加鍾意賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T10:44:45.000Z","msg":"input質素最差"},{"pid":"d2d87d549a745b70f274249e029bdd92896550fb","tid":2194148,"uid":346701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1703539f24fb30fbd82201524dd6febfcbe1d1b9","tid":2194148,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T10:40:01.000Z","msg":"其實點解做狗既比其他紀律部隊更加鍾意賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T10:56:00.000Z","msg":"黑社會人品比正常人差"},{"pid":"4a69a126881103b44f1161f6c0fef3eb3eca56b5","tid":2194148,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1703539f24fb30fbd82201524dd6febfcbe1d1b9","tid":2194148,"uid":66365,"like":0,"